des:
Fun interactive dancing game for kids aged 3+. If your kid likes dancing, they will love kid dancer!

Kid Dancer includes six fun levels:
*Jungle
*Outer Space
*Desert
*City
*Ocean
*Fairyland

Loved by ages: 3-8!
